05重 6:17 You must diligently keep the commandments of the LORD your God, and his decrees, and his statutes that he has commanded you.
05重 6:18 Do what is right and good in the sight of the LORD, so that it may go well with you, and so that you may go in and occupy the good land that the LORD swore to your ancestors to give you,
05重 6:19 thrusting out all your enemies from before you, as the LORD has promised.
05重 6:20 When your children ask you in time to come, "What is the meaning of the decrees and the statutes and the ordinances that the LORD our God has commanded you?"
