05重 6:22 The LORD displayed before our eyes great and awesome signs and wonders against Egypt, against Pharaoh and all his household.
05重 6:23 He brought us out from there in order to bring us in, to give us the land that he promised on oath to our ancestors.
05重 6:24 Then the LORD commanded us to observe all these statutes, to fear the LORD our God, for our lasting good, so as to keep us alive, as is now the case.
