05重 8:9 a land where you may eat bread without scarcity, where you will lack nothing, a land whose stones are iron and from whose hills you may mine copper.
05重 8:10 You shall eat your fill and bless the LORD your God for the good land that he has given you.
05重 8:11 Take care that you do not forget the LORD your God, by failing to keep his commandments, his ordinances, and his statutes, which I am commanding you today.
05重 8:12 When you have eaten your fill and have built fine houses and live in them,
