05重 11:16 Take care, or you will be seduced into turning away, serving other gods and worshiping them,
05重 11:17 for then the anger of the LORD will be kindled against you and he will shut up the heavens, so that there will be no rain and the land will yield no fruit; then you will perish quickly off the good land that the LORD is giving you.
