05重 13:14 then you shall inquire and make a thorough investigation. If the charge is established that such an abhorrent thing has been done among you,
05重 13:15 you shall put the inhabitants of that town to the sword, utterly destroying it and everything in it--even putting its livestock to the sword.
05重 13:16 All of its spoil you shall gather into its public square; then burn the town and all its spoil with fire, as a whole burnt offering to the LORD your God. It shall remain a perpetual ruin, never to be rebuilt.
