07資 6:1 The Israelites did what was evil in the sight of the LORD, and the LORD gave them into the hand of Midian seven years.
07資 6:2 The hand of Midian prevailed over Israel; and because of Midian the Israelites provided for themselves hiding places in the mountains, caves and strongholds.
07資 6:3 For whenever the Israelites put in seed, the Midianites and the Amalekites and the people of the East would come up against them.
